de.rincewind.api.gui.elements

Interface ElementScanner

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Element, ElementSlot, EventBased
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CraftElementScanner, Elements.ElementScannerExtendable

    public interface ElementScanner
extends ElementSlot
    The element allows you to scan the item laying in the slot. In the constructor the ClickBlocker of this element will be automatically unlocked with ClickBlocker.unlock().
    Since:
    2.3.3
    Author:
    Rincewind34
